author: Lauren Levinson
title: There Are More Too Faced Peach Products Coming to Sephora!
text:
New Too Faced Peach Products 2017 There Are More Too Faced Peach Products Coming to Sephora! March 13, 2017 A post shared by Jerrod Blandino (@jerrodblandino) on Mar 12, 2017 at 12:27pm PDT 
It's a peach revolution! Too Faced founder Jerrod Blandino just leaked that there are more peach products coming exclusively to Sephora. The offering already includes blush, eye shadow, bronzer, highlighter, and lip oil . This first iteration grew a crazy-obsessed fan base instantly. 
The new lineup seems to include more palettes (cream blush?), bottles (primer?), and lipstick tubes. Hard to tell, but we'd love to hear your guesses on what's inside the pretty packaging. 
Fans are already freaking out. One Instagrammer wrote: "What?!? How am I supposed to remain calm?!" 
Since peach makeup is the hottest trend of Spring 2017 , you're going to need to get all of these on your face when they launch. We reached out to Too Faced for more info, and we will keep you posted as details emerge! ADVERTISEMENT A post shared by Jerrod Blandino (@jerrodblandino) on Mar 12, 2017 at 12:16pm PDT
